WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.869
Hey, good morning, family. How are you

00:00:02.869 --> 00:00:02.879
all

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:04.870
doing today? I have some things on my

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:07.150
heart to talk to you all about. First

00:00:07.160 --> 00:00:08.950
off, I just want to say thank you for all

00:00:08.960 --> 00:00:11.830
the people who are liking

00:00:11.830 --> 00:00:11.840
and subscribing;

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.190
you are such a

00:00:14.200 --> 00:00:16.390
blessing to us. I mean, I think my channel

00:00:16.400 --> 00:00:19.710
went in the last two weeks from 125,000

00:00:19.720 --> 00:00:22.189
to 130-something thousand now, and I

00:00:22.199 --> 00:00:24.950
give all the glory to God. You know,

00:00:24.960 --> 00:00:26.630
people want to say, 'Brandon, are you a

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:29.790
prophet? Are you a watcher? Who are

00:00:29.790 --> 00:00:29.800
you?'And

00:00:29.800 --> 00:00:31.950
I just want to tell everybody now,

00:00:31.960 --> 00:00:34.350
I'm just a person who prays. I

00:00:34.360 --> 00:00:36.630
don't label myself as anything; I just

00:00:36.640 --> 00:00:39.630
want to let everybody know I just

00:00:39.640 --> 00:00:43.389
love Jesus, and that's all that matters.

00:00:43.389 --> 00:00:43.399
If

00:00:43.399 --> 00:00:45.510
anybody wants to label me

00:00:45.510 --> 00:00:45.520
anything—like

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.389
with the interview of Chris

00:00:47.389 --> 00:00:47.399
yesterday—people

00:00:47.399 --> 00:00:48.950
say, 'You're a

00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:48.960
prophet,'or

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:50.910
'You're this, you're

00:00:50.910 --> 00:00:50.920
that.'No,

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.750
I'm a person just like you

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:56.270
all. I come on here and I tell everybody

00:00:56.280 --> 00:00:58.430
that Jesus is coming, and that's all that

00:00:58.440 --> 00:01:00.470
I want to be called. I don't need a

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:03.470
platform. I don't need my name

00:01:03.470 --> 00:01:03.480
in

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:05.950
lights. I just want Jesus to be excited

00:01:05.960 --> 00:01:07.990
about me when I cross over, and that's

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.310
all that matters to me. I want to

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:11.990
tell you all this; this is very

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.710
important that you understand. The

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:16.910
Lord gave me this revelation.

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.510
I wasn't going to go down this path,

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.910
but it just came

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:23.950
up. People are so focused

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:30.069
on being something big in this life,

00:01:30.079 --> 00:01:31.389
and you're missing

00:01:31.399 --> 00:01:35.789
it. If you want popularity, and if you're

00:01:35.799 --> 00:01:39.310
wanting the world system to acknowledge

00:01:39.310 --> 00:01:39.320
you—fame,

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:43.950
money,

00:01:43.950 --> 00:01:43.960
success—all

00:01:43.960 --> 00:01:47.789
that, you're in trouble. People need to

00:01:47.799 --> 00:01:50.469
understand that this life is a vapor, and

00:01:50.479 --> 00:01:54.310
we all see that. I feel like

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:57.109
the older I get, the time

00:01:57.119 --> 00:01:59.590
seems to be going faster and faster.

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:01.630
But one night I was praying, and the Lord

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:04.310
showed me into the thousand-year ruling

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:06.310
and reigning. He said the last will be

00:02:06.320 --> 00:02:09.150
first, and the first will be last. A

00:02:09.160 --> 00:02:11.670
lot of people that feel they're

00:02:11.680 --> 00:02:14.509
going to have great rewards in heaven

00:02:14.519 --> 00:02:17.750
are going to be shocked because of the

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:21.550
fact that you did it all for praise on

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:24.229
the

00:02:24.239 --> 00:02:28.030
earth. The Bible says that he that sows in

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:30.790
secret will be rewarded

00:02:30.800 --> 00:02:33.910
openly. Even Jesus

00:02:33.920 --> 00:02:36.030
said praying in

00:02:36.040 --> 00:02:40.309
secret, giving in secret, doing things

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:42.869
without having to have praise on this earth—basically,

00:02:42.869 --> 00:02:42.879
that

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:44.350
is what I'm trying to

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:47.949
talk about: volunteering at the church

00:02:47.959 --> 00:02:50.390
or cleaning a bathroom just because

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:52.949
you love the Lord. You didn't have to

00:02:52.959 --> 00:02:55.910
have people say, 'Look at me, look at me! I just

00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:59.830
gave $10,000 to the

00:02:59.830 --> 00:02:59.840
church!'versus

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.630
the widow who gave two pennies, but

00:03:02.640 --> 00:03:04.390
she gave all she

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:07.470
had. Look at what happened to the people

00:03:07.470 --> 00:03:07.480
in

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:09.750
the story in the Bible;

00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:12.830
Jesus was saying she was

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:18.110
greater, right? So here we are

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:20.990
again: Jesus Christ is the same yesterday,

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:22.630
today, and

00:03:22.640 --> 00:03:26.910
forever. When you do things in

00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:30.630
private unto the Lord, there's more

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:32.910
reward to that. Now, if

00:03:32.920 --> 00:03:34.630
you're doing it, like I said, some people

00:03:34.640 --> 00:03:36.030
want to say, 'Hey, well, I just want to let

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:38.670
you know I gave that person this or

00:03:38.670 --> 00:03:38.680
that,'you

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:40.309
got your reward right there.

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.670
You're not getting anything on the other

00:03:41.680 --> 00:03:44.470
side. I'm just telling you, when we step

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:47.270
over into that thousand years, you are

00:03:47.280 --> 00:03:50.390
going to be shocked when you see who's

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:54.470
first and who's last. People have no

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:57.110
idea the arrogance that they

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:58.910
display in their hearts. The Lord looks

00:03:58.920 --> 00:04:00.869
at the core,

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:04.869
the deep hidden things, the motives of

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:08.550
why you do things, your thoughts, your

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:10.949
intentions; everything, He looks at it. And

00:04:10.959 --> 00:04:13.309
I'm telling you all, He

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:14.589
does it to me all the time. He says,

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:17.030
'Brandon, I'm monitoring your heart.

00:04:17.040 --> 00:04:19.749
I'm watching you.'And even

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:21.229
whenever I have bad thoughts or I'm

00:04:21.239 --> 00:04:24.710
angry, He says, 'Check those thoughts. Change your

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:28.550
thoughts right now.'And I say, 'Oh, yes,

00:04:28.550 --> 00:04:28.560
Lord.'The

00:04:28.560 --> 00:04:32.270
closer you get with Him

00:04:32.280 --> 00:04:35.029
and the closer you walk with Him, He will

00:04:36.639 --> 00:04:38.990
correct those things, and

00:04:39.000 --> 00:04:42.070
it's all to go from glory to glory. So,

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:44.430
I'm going back to this: when you get to

00:04:44.440 --> 00:04:48.990
the other side and you did all

00:04:49.000 --> 00:04:50.710
these things unto the Lord versus

00:04:50.710 --> 00:04:50.720
doing

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:52.430
it for the praise of man or

00:04:52.440 --> 00:04:55.749
because of a wrong motive, I'm telling

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:59.270
you, the Lord showed me. He said

00:04:59.280 --> 00:05:01.830
everything is based on

00:05:01.830 --> 00:05:01.840
seedtime

00:05:01.840 --> 00:05:05.430
and harvest. Everything. Whatever a man

00:05:05.430 --> 00:05:05.440
sows,

00:05:05.440 --> 00:05:09.670
that will he also reap. And

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:12.990
every seed produces after its own kind.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.830
So, whenever He showed me into the

00:05:14.840 --> 00:05:16.590
thousand years, He said,

00:05:16.600 --> 00:05:19.710
'Brandon, what you're sowing every

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.710
single day of your

00:05:21.710 --> 00:05:21.720
life...'Every

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:25.550
day you get up, we all have

00:05:25.550 --> 00:05:25.560
seven

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:27.749
days a week, we all have 24 hours in a

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:31.870
day. What you sow in that time,

00:05:31.880 --> 00:05:35.950
day by day, turns into

00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:38.469
years.

00:05:38.469 --> 00:05:38.479
That

00:05:41.629 --> 00:05:41.639
timeframe

00:05:41.639 --> 00:05:44.070
is

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:46.790
the seed that

00:05:46.800 --> 00:05:49.749
you sowed for the thousand years.

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:53.230
Everything you seed in that timeframe is

00:05:53.230 --> 00:05:53.240
what you

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:55.390
will

00:05:55.390 --> 00:05:55.400
reap—good

00:05:55.400 --> 00:05:57.870
intentions or whatever.

00:05:57.880 --> 00:05:59.990
Your heart

00:05:59.990 --> 00:06:00.000
sowing

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:01.550
that into the thousand years, you're

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:03.870
going to reap it. And the position you

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:06.510
will have in that

00:06:06.510 --> 00:06:06.520
thousand-year

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:08.710
ruling and reigning with Him,

00:06:11.080 --> 00:06:13.790
what you will do in those thousand

00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:13.800
years—I'm

00:06:13.800 --> 00:06:16.589
telling you all, I've seen

00:06:16.589 --> 00:06:16.599
it—it

00:06:16.599 --> 00:06:19.390
will be what you sowed in your life

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:23.589
on this earth. How you walked in love... You

00:06:23.599 --> 00:06:26.029
have to walk in love. People say, 'Oh,

00:06:26.039 --> 00:06:28.230
you're being criticized all over the

00:06:28.240 --> 00:06:30.550
internet; are you going to respond to

00:06:30.550 --> 00:06:30.560
that?'And

00:06:30.560 --> 00:06:35.029
I say no. Love takes no account

00:06:35.039 --> 00:06:38.070
of a suffered wrong. No matter how bad

00:06:38.080 --> 00:06:40.790
somebody runs you down, you don't go back

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:43.790
and attack.

00:06:43.800 --> 00:06:45.110
They have their opinion,

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:47.469
they're entitled to it, but I don't have

00:06:47.479 --> 00:06:49.550
to allow people... They say, 'Why do you

00:06:49.550 --> 00:06:49.560
erase

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:50.749
the comments? Why do you do all this

00:06:50.749 --> 00:06:50.759
stuff?'Because

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:53.189
just as much as this is

00:06:53.199 --> 00:06:54.909
my house, I have to protect my people

00:06:54.919 --> 00:06:56.189
that come in

00:06:56.199 --> 00:06:58.230
here. You're not going to come and

00:06:58.240 --> 00:07:01.270
throw up all over my

00:07:01.280 --> 00:07:03.830
platform. It's my job to keep it, just

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:05.550
like a pastor takes care of his church;

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:07.110
he doesn't allow people to come in and

00:07:07.120 --> 00:07:09.309
just vomit all over the

00:07:09.319 --> 00:07:11.629
aisles and the stage. So, I'm not

00:07:11.639 --> 00:07:13.309
going to allow people to come and vomit in

00:07:13.319 --> 00:07:16.710
here. If you're rude, I erase it. My

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:18.589
son does; I don't have time to read all

00:07:18.599 --> 00:07:20.950
that trash. But I'm going to tell

00:07:20.960 --> 00:07:26.869
you this: my job is to maintain love. Love

00:07:26.879 --> 00:07:30.029
takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:07:30.039 --> 00:07:32.550
Regardless of how somebody is talking bad

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:34.270
about you and running you down on

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:36.110
another channel, the

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:38.350
Bible says pray for those that come

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:41.270
against you. Pray for them.

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:44.029
Love on them, and that's

00:07:44.039 --> 00:07:46.189
what Jesus would do. He didn't

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:47.909
go over there and say, 'Well, you Pharisees,

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:51.510
I'm going

00:07:51.510 --> 00:07:51.520
to

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:52.790
beat

00:07:52.790 --> 00:07:52.800
you

00:07:52.800 --> 00:07:54.309
up.'Jesus

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:57.149
said, 'I love

00:07:57.159 --> 00:08:01.309
you, period. I pray for you.'And so

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:04.510
that's where I have to stay:

00:08:04.520 --> 00:08:08.270
maintain an atmosphere of love because

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:11.589
that's the greater glory. If you want to

00:08:11.599 --> 00:08:14.149
walk in the greater glory, if you want to

00:08:14.159 --> 00:08:16.230
walk in the presence of the

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:19.990
Lord, God is love. It's not just what He does;

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:22.990
it's who He

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:27.230
is. God is love. And I want to

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:29.550
abide in the Lord. 'If you abide in Me

00:08:29.550 --> 00:08:29.560
and

00:08:29.560 --> 00:08:31.270
My words remain in you, you shall ask

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:34.190
what you will and it shall be

00:08:34.190 --> 00:08:34.200
done.'But

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:35.990
God is love, and that has to abide in you,

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:37.790
and you remain in Him. I'm telling

00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:39.630
you, the moment you start getting off of

00:08:39.640 --> 00:08:42.509
that love walk and not walking in love,

00:08:42.519 --> 00:08:44.190
you're letting the devil rule and reign

00:08:44.190 --> 00:08:44.200
over

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:46.389
you. All I can do is keep looking at

00:08:46.399 --> 00:08:49.269
you and saying, 'Lord, help

00:08:49.269 --> 00:08:49.279
me,'because

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:50.949
I want Jesus to flow

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:53.910
through my life. I want Him to shine on

00:08:53.920 --> 00:08:57.070
me. Whenever I stand in this seat, I

00:08:57.080 --> 00:08:59.910
take it seriously. I

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:02.430
pray, and I feel the Lord has told

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:04.350
me to come on here and tell you all

00:09:04.360 --> 00:09:06.790
what He tells me to tell you. Now, if you

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:10.110
think I'm off, like some people do, then

00:09:10.120 --> 00:09:12.550
just click out. Click it off. You

00:09:12.560 --> 00:09:14.430
don't have to be hateful and rude. Just

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:16.389
click off and say, 'You know what?

00:09:16.389 --> 00:09:16.399
Whatever.'My

00:09:16.399 --> 00:09:18.509
job is to just try to

00:09:18.519 --> 00:09:20.030
tell you what I feel like the

00:09:20.030 --> 00:09:20.040
Lord

00:09:20.040 --> 00:09:23.030
told me to tell you. So here's what I

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:24.829
had for you today. That was a little side

00:09:24.839 --> 00:09:27.110
note, but I have something

00:09:27.120 --> 00:09:28.110
more for

00:09:28.120 --> 00:09:30.710
you, and this is important that you

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:34.670
hear. I am not giving glory or

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:38.630
any kind of praise to the devil at

00:09:38.640 --> 00:09:40.670
all; he came

00:09:40.680 --> 00:09:43.870
uninvited. But I want to tell

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:45.430
you this because I feel like it's

00:09:45.440 --> 00:09:47.829
important because people need to

00:09:47.839 --> 00:09:51.269
know some things like this.

00:09:51.279 --> 00:09:54.389
One night I was asleep, and I was

00:09:54.399 --> 00:09:57.190
woken up in the

00:09:57.200 --> 00:10:00.069
middle of the night, about 3:00 in the

00:10:00.079 --> 00:10:02.550
morning, with Satan standing right in

00:10:02.560 --> 00:10:03.910
front of my

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:07.150
bed. At this

00:10:07.160 --> 00:10:10.030
time, I'm going to go into detail—and I

00:10:10.040 --> 00:10:13.110
never do this because he's

00:10:13.120 --> 00:10:16.670
not worthy of it, he is a piece of

00:10:16.670 --> 00:10:16.680
trash—but

00:10:16.680 --> 00:10:21.310
people need to

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:24.710
understand more in detail about things.

00:10:24.720 --> 00:10:26.750
I think a lot

00:10:26.760 --> 00:10:28.150
of times

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:33.069
the body of Christ is real ignorant

00:10:33.069 --> 00:10:33.079
of

00:10:33.079 --> 00:10:34.870
a lot of things of the spirit.

00:10:34.880 --> 00:10:37.110
I try to just brush over

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.030
things sometimes, but I felt in my spirit

00:10:39.040 --> 00:10:41.350
today to go into more detail about

00:10:41.360 --> 00:10:42.790
things,

00:10:42.800 --> 00:10:45.470
and then I'm going to go

00:10:45.480 --> 00:10:47.750
somewhere else with it. So, I just want

00:10:47.760 --> 00:10:48.670
you to

00:10:48.680 --> 00:10:53.190
listen. I was woken up out of my sleep,

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:56.230
and the devil was standing right there.

00:10:56.240 --> 00:10:57.829
I'm going to describe

00:10:57.839 --> 00:11:02.590
him to you: he is beautiful. His hair

00:11:02.600 --> 00:11:06.030
is flowing down to his shoulders, but it

00:11:06.040 --> 00:11:11.069
is very beautiful. The layers of him...

00:11:11.079 --> 00:11:14.870
The way his face was,

00:11:14.880 --> 00:11:18.629
it draws you in. His eyes were

00:11:18.639 --> 00:11:22.870
as black as

00:11:22.870 --> 00:11:22.880
onyx—the

00:11:22.880 --> 00:11:27.389
blackest, most evil eyes I've ever seen.

00:11:27.399 --> 00:11:29.910
It was

00:11:29.920 --> 00:11:36.509
just pure evil. But his face and

00:11:36.519 --> 00:11:41.949
his voice... His voice sounded like

00:11:41.959 --> 00:11:46.350
music. This is very interesting. The pitch

00:11:46.360 --> 00:11:48.910
of his voice was

00:11:48.920 --> 00:11:53.030
perfect. The way his voice carried

00:11:53.040 --> 00:11:54.829
when he spoke to

00:11:54.839 --> 00:11:57.389
me, it sounded

00:11:57.399 --> 00:11:59.949
like

00:12:02.360 --> 00:12:04.710
a symphony.

00:12:04.720 --> 00:12:06.470
It didn't sound like musical

00:12:06.480 --> 00:12:11.750
instruments playing; it carried perfect

00:12:11.760 --> 00:12:14.389
pitch. The way it hit my ears when I

00:12:14.399 --> 00:12:16.949
heard it, it was

00:12:16.959 --> 00:12:20.870
soothing. His

00:12:20.880 --> 00:12:24.069
clothes were flowing, and it almost looked

00:12:24.079 --> 00:12:26.189
like one of those

00:12:26.199 --> 00:12:27.949
commercials when you put

00:12:27.959 --> 00:12:30.150
the fan in front of the model's face and

00:12:30.160 --> 00:12:32.350
the hair is blowing and it's very

00:12:35.230 --> 00:12:35.240
dramatic—they

00:12:37.160 --> 00:12:39.430
flip their hair

00:12:39.430 --> 00:12:39.440
and

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:42.030
the wind is blowing in it

00:12:42.040 --> 00:12:44.350
like a fan. It was like that because his

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.389
hair was

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:47.550
moving like it was

00:12:47.560 --> 00:12:52.189
alive. But he had a light around

00:12:52.199 --> 00:12:56.550
him. He comes as an angel of

00:12:56.550 --> 00:12:56.560
light—deceitful.

00:12:56.560 --> 00:13:01.110
He's trying to mimic

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:05.430
everything that God is. He's so evil, but

00:13:05.440 --> 00:13:10.110
he comes as if he's good, but he is

00:13:10.120 --> 00:13:12.550
not.

00:13:12.560 --> 00:13:15.150
He is deceitful, and he's an accuser of

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:16.870
the

00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:20.310
brethren. At this time,

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:22.470
I was laying

00:13:22.480 --> 00:13:26.310
there, and I was frozen in my bed with the

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:28.110
most fear I've ever felt in my whole

00:13:28.120 --> 00:13:29.269
entire life. I'm just being

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:32.750
real with you all; I couldn't move. I was

00:13:32.760 --> 00:13:35.230
just locked. You know when

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:38.110
you come up on a

00:13:38.120 --> 00:13:40.990
dog or something very dangerous, like a

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:43.430
poisonous snake, your

00:13:43.440 --> 00:13:46.710
body and adrenaline are flowing so strong

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:50.069
you just lock?

00:13:50.079 --> 00:13:51.829
That's the way I felt.

00:13:51.839 --> 00:13:54.590
I just froze and I started

00:13:54.600 --> 00:13:56.509
praying underneath my breath. I was

00:13:56.509 --> 00:13:56.519
saying,

00:13:56.519 --> 00:13:59.269
'In the name of Jesus, get out of my

00:13:59.279 --> 00:14:02.069
house. In the name of Jesus, get out of my

00:14:02.069 --> 00:14:02.079
house.'But

00:14:02.079 --> 00:14:05.069
I was saying it out of so much

00:14:05.079 --> 00:14:08.870
fear. He started laughing at me, and he

00:14:08.880 --> 00:14:10.350
was

00:14:10.360 --> 00:14:13.189
cackling the whole time.

00:14:13.199 --> 00:14:16.069
He said, 'I've

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:18.590
come with a message for you. I'm

00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:21.590
going to offer you something.'At this

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:24.629
time I'm just frozen, not

00:14:24.639 --> 00:14:26.430
knowing what to do. This is what I think

00:14:26.430 --> 00:14:26.440
is

00:14:26.440 --> 00:14:29.310
interesting:

00:14:33.079 --> 00:14:35.509
when you're

00:14:35.519 --> 00:14:37.870
seeing over in the spirit, he used the

00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:40.670
gift that I have, the prophetic, to be

00:14:40.680 --> 00:14:42.470
able to attain it. With seeing over in

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:45.189
the spirit with the

00:14:45.199 --> 00:14:48.509
demonic, I was shown a vision. Now, he presented this to me, and in

00:14:48.509 --> 00:14:48.519
the spirit, I saw it as a vision. I

00:14:48.519 --> 00:14:50.629
see

00:14:50.629 --> 00:14:50.639
this

00:14:50.639 --> 00:14:53.590
vision

00:15:00.639 --> 00:15:03.110
of all this, and he

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:05.430
says, 'I'm going to offer you

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:07.350
anything and everything if you bow your

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:10.670
knee to me and you worship

00:15:10.670 --> 00:15:10.680
me.'He

00:15:10.680 --> 00:15:12.749
said, 'I will give you your

00:15:12.759 --> 00:15:14.550
heart's desires of everything and

00:15:14.560 --> 00:15:17.230
anything you ever wanted.'And he showed

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:20.310
me. I could see cars—Ferraris,

00:15:20.310 --> 00:15:20.320
Lamborghinis—massive

00:15:20.320 --> 00:15:23.550
houses on the

00:15:23.560 --> 00:15:26.670
ocean, all this stuff, piles of cash. I

00:15:26.680 --> 00:15:28.749
could see piles of cash.

00:15:28.749 --> 00:15:28.759
He

00:15:28.759 --> 00:15:31.110
showed me all this

00:15:31.120 --> 00:15:34.790
wealth, a yacht—massive

00:15:34.790 --> 00:15:34.800
yachts—everything

00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:36.870
that your fleshly

00:15:36.880 --> 00:15:39.990
desires

00:15:40.000 --> 00:15:42.749
would ever imagine. He had it

00:15:42.759 --> 00:15:45.230
all spread out.

00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:47.470
'If you bow your knee and you use your

00:15:47.480 --> 00:15:50.389
giftings for me, I will make you

00:15:50.389 --> 00:15:50.399
wealthy

00:15:50.399 --> 00:15:51.670
beyond anything you could ever

00:15:51.680 --> 00:15:53.189
comprehend.'So,

00:15:53.199 --> 00:15:56.470
he takes me in, and I

00:15:56.480 --> 00:16:00.990
see this massive palace. It's

00:16:00.990 --> 00:16:01.000
the

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:04.110
most evil, but he tried to make it

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:06.110
look beautiful.

00:16:06.120 --> 00:16:10.150
It was black

00:16:10.150 --> 00:16:10.160
onyx—his

00:16:10.160 --> 00:16:12.430
throne. Not an altar;

00:16:12.440 --> 00:16:15.150
it was a

00:16:15.150 --> 00:16:15.160
throne—a

00:16:15.160 --> 00:16:19.749
throne that was pure black

00:16:19.749 --> 00:16:19.759
onyx

00:16:19.759 --> 00:16:23.230
with red rubies

00:16:23.240 --> 00:16:25.829
and diamonds on it.

00:16:25.839 --> 00:16:29.509
But

00:16:29.519 --> 00:16:31.230
remember I told you I went to the throne

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:33.870
room with the Father? The Lord

00:16:33.880 --> 00:16:37.710
showed me His throne. He tried to

00:16:37.720 --> 00:16:42.350
mimic and mock the Lord's throne. But I

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:45.470
told you living water was flowing from

00:16:45.480 --> 00:16:48.430
the Father's

00:16:48.430 --> 00:16:48.440
throne—the

00:16:48.440 --> 00:16:52.350
most beautiful, clear crystal water was

00:16:52.360 --> 00:16:54.350
flowing out of the throne of God, and it

00:16:54.360 --> 00:16:57.629
was coming into a massive pool on the

00:16:57.639 --> 00:17:00.710
bottom of

00:17:05.079 --> 00:17:06.990
the steps of the Father. There was

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:08.909
beautiful water, and it was living water.

00:17:12.199 --> 00:17:15.270
Well, down the devil's

00:17:15.280 --> 00:17:19.870
throne was blood, and there was a pool of

00:17:19.880 --> 00:17:22.870
blood at the bottom of the steps. It looked like

00:17:22.880 --> 00:17:25.510
red-looking,

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:30.029
nasty stuff flowing down

00:17:30.029 --> 00:17:30.039
the

00:17:30.039 --> 00:17:33.350
steps of this place. In the

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:36.950
front,

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:39.150
it opened up and

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:43.230
then there were these two

00:17:43.230 --> 00:17:43.240
black-looking

00:17:43.240 --> 00:17:45.110
pillars.

00:17:45.120 --> 00:17:48.990
It

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:50.390
looked like marble because it was like

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:52.870
the Roman

00:17:52.880 --> 00:17:55.590
Coliseum, the way that was all designed.

00:17:55.600 --> 00:17:57.950
It's all

00:17:57.960 --> 00:17:59.430
chiseled out

00:17:59.440 --> 00:18:02.270
like those

00:18:02.280 --> 00:18:05.710
Greek columns inside

00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:07.750
his throne room.

00:18:07.760 --> 00:18:09.750
There were

00:18:09.750 --> 00:18:09.760
all

00:18:09.760 --> 00:18:12.750
these pillars going straight

00:18:12.760 --> 00:18:14.870
up; I could see the pillars in the spirit

00:18:14.870 --> 00:18:14.880
realm.

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:18.390
The floor had the pool of

00:18:18.400 --> 00:18:21.630
blood, and it was all right before

00:18:21.640 --> 00:18:25.470
his throne. He had this decoration

00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:28.230
stuff; of course, he's satanic,

00:18:28.240 --> 00:18:29.390
he's the devil.

00:18:29.400 --> 00:18:31.430
But it was all around the floor; it was

00:18:31.440 --> 00:18:34.149
like this marble and

00:18:34.159 --> 00:18:37.470
everything. He was trying to show all

00:18:37.480 --> 00:18:40.029
his wealth of what was his

00:18:40.039 --> 00:18:40.990
in the

00:18:41.000 --> 00:18:44.870
earth. All I could do at this time

00:18:44.880 --> 00:18:47.630
whenever he was offering me this... I

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:51.470
spoke out loud and said, 'I will never

00:18:51.480 --> 00:18:55.669
bow my knee to you, and I will never

00:18:55.679 --> 00:18:57.630
give my heart over to

00:18:57.630 --> 00:18:57.640
you.'There's

00:18:57.640 --> 00:18:59.990
nothing that you

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:02.470
could offer me that I would ever want.

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:04.870
I was

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:07.110
so angry at this moment because I

00:19:07.110 --> 00:19:07.120
was

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:09.950
frozen in fear.

00:19:09.960 --> 00:19:11.149
And there's a lot of you that

00:19:11.159 --> 00:19:12.750
don't believe in the baptism of the Holy

00:19:12.760 --> 00:19:14.750
Spirit and speaking in other

00:19:14.760 --> 00:19:17.870
tongues, but I do believe it, and I

00:19:17.880 --> 00:19:21.310
practice this daily. All of a sudden,

00:19:21.320 --> 00:19:24.190
I just started praying in the spirit.

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:25.669
The Lord told me,

00:19:25.679 --> 00:19:28.190
'Brandon, you have to pray in the spirit

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:30.789
and you have to build yourself up right

00:19:30.789 --> 00:19:30.799
now.'And

00:19:30.799 --> 00:19:32.750
I started praying in

00:19:36.159 --> 00:19:38.830
tongues. And what seemed like literally the

00:19:38.840 --> 00:19:41.750
whole time I'm praying in tongues, he's

00:19:41.760 --> 00:19:45.430
laughing at me and he's mocking me.

00:19:45.440 --> 00:19:47.590
It was like a

00:19:47.590 --> 00:19:47.600
cackle—the

00:19:47.600 --> 00:19:50.789
Michael Jackson Thriller laugh—the whole

00:19:50.799 --> 00:19:53.310
time he's laughing, and I'm telling you,

00:19:53.320 --> 00:19:57.070
it was so loud it felt like it was echoing

00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:59.270
in my house.

00:19:59.280 --> 00:20:02.310
My son will play

00:20:02.320 --> 00:20:03.470
what it sounded like; it sounded like

00:20:03.480 --> 00:20:05.190
Michael

00:20:05.200 --> 00:20:06.950
Jackson's

00:20:06.960 --> 00:20:08.830
'Thriller.'He's

00:20:08.840 --> 00:20:10.990
laughing at me, and I'm praying in

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:12.870
the spirit.

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:17.110
I said, 'In the name of Jesus, get out of

00:20:17.120 --> 00:20:18.710
my house!'And he's just laughing. But I'm

00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:22.710
in fear, and fear tolerated is faith

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:25.350
contaminated. When you're

00:20:25.360 --> 00:20:27.710
operating in fear, you're not operating

00:20:27.720 --> 00:20:30.390
in faith because you have more

00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:32.390
faith in the ability of the devil to hurt you than you have faith in

00:20:33.919 --> 00:20:35.430
God to protect you.

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:38.470
Fear is fear of

00:20:38.480 --> 00:20:41.070
death. So I'm in fear of him,

00:20:41.080 --> 00:20:42.549
and at that moment I'm

00:20:42.559 --> 00:20:44.430
freaking out. But I'm praying in the

00:20:44.440 --> 00:20:46.149
spirit, and I'm just praying, and

00:20:46.159 --> 00:20:48.230
it felt like it was forever. All of

00:20:48.230 --> 00:20:48.240
a sudden, I

00:20:48.240 --> 00:20:50.870
just

00:20:52.799 --> 00:20:54.909
felt that bubbling, that fire come up out

00:20:54.919 --> 00:20:59.270
of my belly, and I said, 'In the name

00:20:59.280 --> 00:21:04.070
of Jesus, you get out of my house

00:21:04.070 --> 00:21:04.080
now!'And

00:21:04.080 --> 00:21:06.230
all of a sudden, everything

00:21:06.240 --> 00:21:08.430
went, and he disappeared right in front

00:21:08.440 --> 00:21:09.549
of my

00:21:09.559 --> 00:21:12.230
face because fire came up out of my

00:21:12.240 --> 00:21:15.110
belly. Out of your belly shall flow

00:21:15.120 --> 00:21:17.950
rivers of living water. You have

00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:20.549
authority over the devil, but you have to

00:21:20.559 --> 00:21:22.710
understand who you are in Christ, and you

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:24.830
can't be in fear.

00:21:24.840 --> 00:21:26.510
You have to build yourself up by

00:21:26.520 --> 00:21:27.909
praying in the spirit. You have to

00:21:27.919 --> 00:21:29.590
understand that Word and get that Word

00:21:29.600 --> 00:21:31.830
down inside of your heart. You have to

00:21:31.840 --> 00:21:33.630
understand that greater is He that is in

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:35.990
you than he that is in the world. You

00:21:36.000 --> 00:21:38.390
can't be afraid because when the devil

00:21:38.390 --> 00:21:38.400
shows

00:21:38.400 --> 00:21:40.149
up like that, you've got to

00:21:40.159 --> 00:21:41.870
understand who you are and you don't

00:21:41.880 --> 00:21:45.470
entertain it. But this is where I

00:21:45.480 --> 00:21:47.390
thought was interesting.

00:21:49.600 --> 00:21:52.950
How do you know when the

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:55.149
devil comes and gives you a vision?

00:21:55.159 --> 00:21:56.630
Because people say, 'How? The devil's

00:21:56.640 --> 00:21:59.110
giving him

00:21:59.110 --> 00:21:59.120
visions.'The

00:21:59.120 --> 00:22:00.029
devil

00:22:00.029 --> 00:22:00.039
is

00:22:00.039 --> 00:22:02.710
giving you these things;

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:04.549
he's a messenger of

00:22:04.559 --> 00:22:07.029
the devil, he's not a prophet of God.

00:22:08.679 --> 00:22:11.510
I've seen that side.

00:22:12.880 --> 00:22:14.630
You know how you

00:22:14.640 --> 00:22:17.669
know the difference between the Lord and

00:22:17.679 --> 00:22:19.390
the

00:22:19.400 --> 00:22:22.990
devil? You can get snared very easily by

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:25.470
a familiar spirit messing with the

00:22:25.480 --> 00:22:27.269
way the Lord has

00:22:27.279 --> 00:22:30.110
allowed me to, with my

00:22:30.120 --> 00:22:32.750
prophetic gifting and being a watchman.

00:22:32.760 --> 00:22:35.430
You have to be in the presence of the

00:22:35.440 --> 00:22:38.149
Lord through worship and His Word.

00:22:38.159 --> 00:22:41.830
You will have to

00:22:41.840 --> 00:22:44.070
know when you're operating in the

00:22:44.080 --> 00:22:45.950
pureness of the gift, which is when you're

00:22:45.960 --> 00:22:48.750
under the glory. When you are underneath

00:22:48.760 --> 00:22:51.149
the presence in worship and you are

00:22:51.159 --> 00:22:54.110
reading your Bible and you're praying,

00:22:54.120 --> 00:22:57.470
there is not a devil in hell that comes

00:22:57.480 --> 00:22:59.070
like that.

00:23:02.070 --> 00:23:02.080
When

00:23:05.320 --> 00:23:07.909
that glory

00:23:07.919 --> 00:23:09.669
comes in and that's whenever you start

00:23:09.669 --> 00:23:09.679
seeing

00:23:09.679 --> 00:23:12.909
over, you will get

00:23:12.919 --> 00:23:14.310
snared if you're just going around

00:23:14.320 --> 00:23:16.269
saying, 'I'm seeing stuff, I'm seeing

00:23:16.269 --> 00:23:16.279
stuff.'You're

00:23:16.279 --> 00:23:17.830
going to get snared by a demonic

00:23:17.840 --> 00:23:19.350
spirit, and it's very

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:22.669
easy to do. You have got to maintain...

00:23:22.679 --> 00:23:24.430
when you're underneath

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:26.710
worship

00:23:26.710 --> 00:23:26.720
and

00:23:26.720 --> 00:23:28.630
it's

00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:30.830
pure and it's coming out of you and you

00:23:30.840 --> 00:23:33.549
get under that

00:23:36.840 --> 00:23:39.750
river of praise and worship and you

00:23:39.760 --> 00:23:42.390
start seeking the Father and you're

00:23:42.400 --> 00:23:44.269
praying and you're speaking in tongues

00:23:44.279 --> 00:23:47.029
and

00:23:47.039 --> 00:23:49.029
He starts showing you things...

00:23:51.760 --> 00:23:55.870
that's how you know.

00:23:57.960 --> 00:24:00.149
You get over in the spirit by praying in

00:24:00.159 --> 00:24:02.630
tongues, and you get in there and worship,

00:24:02.640 --> 00:24:04.470
and you get in the Bible, and then you

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:07.269
say, 'Father, show me scriptures to back up

00:24:07.279 --> 00:24:10.110
what I'm seeing.

00:24:10.120 --> 00:24:12.230
Give me a

00:24:12.240 --> 00:24:14.590
scripture to back up,'because I'm not going

00:24:14.600 --> 00:24:17.350
to get snared by some kind of devil

00:24:17.360 --> 00:24:19.350
coming in here trying to tell me

00:24:19.360 --> 00:24:21.070
something.

00:24:21.080 --> 00:24:23.190
You have to

00:24:23.200 --> 00:24:25.149
get in the river of praise and

00:24:25.159 --> 00:24:27.789
worship and you have to get in the Word

00:24:27.799 --> 00:24:31.990
and test the spirits.

00:24:32.000 --> 00:24:33.389
Test the

00:24:33.399 --> 00:24:35.110
spirits and see whether they are of God

00:24:35.120 --> 00:24:36.830
or not. If it doesn't line up, you're

00:24:36.840 --> 00:24:39.269
going to... and I tell you this: you'll

00:24:39.279 --> 00:24:41.710
have peace that passes understanding.

00:24:41.720 --> 00:24:44.510
The Bible says the sheep

00:24:44.520 --> 00:24:46.110
will know the Shepherd's voice and a

00:24:46.120 --> 00:24:48.590
stranger's voice he'll not follow. But

00:24:48.600 --> 00:24:49.950
when you're hearing the

00:24:49.960 --> 00:24:53.350
devil, there's torment because fear has

00:24:53.360 --> 00:24:56.149
torment. He is a

00:24:56.159 --> 00:24:58.029
devil that torments.

00:24:58.039 --> 00:24:59.669
That's why I say

00:24:59.679 --> 00:25:00.950
a lot of times, 'How do you know

00:25:00.960 --> 00:25:03.510
that's God?'Because they have

00:25:03.520 --> 00:25:06.190
peace. He said He will have perfect

00:25:06.200 --> 00:25:07.909
peace whose mind is stayed on

00:25:07.909 --> 00:25:07.919
Him

00:25:07.919 --> 00:25:10.310
because he's trusting in Him.

00:25:11.880 --> 00:25:13.190
How do you have peace if

00:25:13.200 --> 00:25:15.669
you're seeing destruction and

00:25:15.679 --> 00:25:17.470
a pestilence? You have peace because

00:25:17.470 --> 00:25:17.480
He is the Prince of

00:25:17.480 --> 00:25:19.110
Peace. When

00:25:21.640 --> 00:25:24.310
He flows

00:25:24.320 --> 00:25:26.389
with you and you abide in Him

00:25:26.389 --> 00:25:26.399
and His

00:25:26.399 --> 00:25:28.909
words remain in you...

00:25:28.919 --> 00:25:30.909
when you're

00:25:30.919 --> 00:25:32.630
close to the vine and you're close to

00:25:32.640 --> 00:25:34.230
Him and you're with the

00:25:34.240 --> 00:25:39.350
Father, you will have peace. You have

00:25:39.360 --> 00:25:41.750
joy, you have patience, you have kindness,

00:25:41.760 --> 00:25:43.870
you have goodness, you have self-control

00:25:43.880 --> 00:25:48.110
because He is love.

00:25:48.120 --> 00:25:50.070
That's how I do it.

00:25:50.080 --> 00:25:51.269
That's how

00:25:53.720 --> 00:25:56.590
you do it: you follow the

00:25:56.600 --> 00:25:59.789
voice of the Lord when you walk in love,

00:25:59.799 --> 00:26:02.310
when you pray in the spirit, and

00:26:02.320 --> 00:26:04.630
you read your Bible and you

00:26:04.640 --> 00:26:07.389
fellowship with Him with worship.

00:26:07.399 --> 00:26:09.789
He said He inhabits

00:26:09.799 --> 00:26:11.389
the praises of His

00:26:11.399 --> 00:26:13.590
people.

00:26:13.600 --> 00:26:17.149
That's how I keep

00:26:17.159 --> 00:26:20.110
myself clean. That's how I keep myself

00:26:20.120 --> 00:26:22.950
right before Him. And

00:26:22.960 --> 00:26:25.269
volunteering... don't take

00:26:25.269 --> 00:26:25.279
any

00:26:25.279 --> 00:26:27.430
praise from Him; don't take any glory.

00:26:27.440 --> 00:26:30.149
Always know that we have this treasure in

00:26:30.149 --> 00:26:30.159
earthen

00:26:30.159 --> 00:26:32.190
vessels so that

00:26:32.190 --> 00:26:32.200
the excellence

00:26:32.200 --> 00:26:33.950
of the power might be

00:26:33.960 --> 00:26:37.389
known of Him and not of me.

00:26:39.000 --> 00:26:43.070
I have this treasure

00:26:43.080 --> 00:26:46.110
of Jesus in this

00:26:46.110 --> 00:26:46.120
earthen

00:26:46.120 --> 00:26:49.549
vessel, but the excellence of

00:26:49.559 --> 00:26:52.110
His power will be known of Him. It's

00:26:52.120 --> 00:26:55.310
about Him and it's not about me.

00:26:55.320 --> 00:26:58.470
If you

00:26:58.480 --> 00:27:01.230
always keep your heart right before Him

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:03.029
and you always give Him praise, He'll

00:27:03.039 --> 00:27:05.110
come and visit you. But if you start

00:27:05.120 --> 00:27:07.590
taking His glory, if you start taking

00:27:07.600 --> 00:27:09.830
what belongs to Him like the devil

00:27:09.840 --> 00:27:12.110
did, He's going to cast you

00:27:12.120 --> 00:27:15.310
out.

00:27:15.320 --> 00:27:16.950
Look at what the

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:19.149
devil did: he tried to say he

00:27:19.159 --> 00:27:21.830
exalted himself above God. He wanted

00:27:21.840 --> 00:27:24.990
to become like God; he wanted to be most

00:27:25.000 --> 00:27:28.750
powerful, and he fell like lightning.

00:27:28.760 --> 00:27:32.029
Just always know that you never touch

00:27:32.039 --> 00:27:32.909
God's

00:27:32.919 --> 00:27:37.149
glory. Always

00:27:37.159 --> 00:27:39.830
keep yourself humble before Him, and in

00:27:39.840 --> 00:27:42.909
due time He will exalt you.

00:27:42.919 --> 00:27:44.669
Always keep

00:27:44.679 --> 00:27:46.750
yourself small in your own eyes, and you

00:27:46.760 --> 00:27:48.909
keep walking with Him, and He'll

00:27:48.919 --> 00:27:51.190
come and share His secrets with you

00:27:51.200 --> 00:27:53.590
because He knows He can trust you.

00:28:29.640 --> 00:28:32.110
People think they can fool Him. It's

00:28:32.120 --> 00:28:35.350
silly. God knows your future

00:28:35.360 --> 00:28:36.950
more than you know your

00:28:36.960 --> 00:28:38.509
past,

00:28:38.519 --> 00:28:41.590
and you can't

00:28:41.600 --> 00:28:44.470
pull a fast one over on Him.

00:28:44.470 --> 00:28:44.480
This is

00:28:44.480 --> 00:28:46.269
interesting.

00:28:52.440 --> 00:28:54.470
A lot of people

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:56.590
say, 'The devil's talking to

00:28:56.590 --> 00:28:56.600
me.'The

00:28:56.600 --> 00:28:59.190
devil's a fallen angel.

00:28:59.200 --> 00:29:02.630
So if you can hear the devil's

00:29:02.640 --> 00:29:04.950
voice in the spirit

00:29:04.960 --> 00:29:08.149
realm, you can hear your angel's voice

00:29:08.159 --> 00:29:10.909
in the spirit realm. But

00:29:10.909 --> 00:29:10.919
an

00:29:10.919 --> 00:29:14.070
angel will

00:29:14.080 --> 00:29:17.389
never come and talk to you just to

00:29:17.389 --> 00:29:17.399
talk—like,

00:29:17.399 --> 00:29:21.909
'Hey, let's go hang out.'An angel is

00:29:21.919 --> 00:29:24.710
there on an assignment to warn you about

00:29:24.720 --> 00:29:27.230
something if need be. The Holy Spirit

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:29.029
tells you a lot of things inside of you,

00:29:29.039 --> 00:29:31.029
but if he comes to

00:29:31.029 --> 00:29:31.039
you—you

00:29:31.039 --> 00:29:32.950
entertain angels unaware—they'll come

00:29:32.960 --> 00:29:35.110
and say, 'Listen, don't go this

00:29:35.110 --> 00:29:35.120
way,'and

00:29:35.120 --> 00:29:36.909
he's trying to really protect you.

00:29:36.919 --> 00:29:38.310
They're sent to

00:29:38.320 --> 00:29:40.669
protect us, but they're not there to hang

00:29:40.679 --> 00:29:43.070
out with you and to be your friend. So

00:29:43.080 --> 00:29:44.269
don't be going around saying, 'I'm going

00:29:44.279 --> 00:29:45.630
to hang out with my angel

00:29:45.640 --> 00:29:47.110
today,'because

00:29:47.120 --> 00:29:48.710
you'll

00:29:48.720 --> 00:29:51.230
get snared by a familiar spirit. Angels

00:29:51.240 --> 00:29:53.509
are there on assignment to protect you. I

00:29:53.509 --> 00:29:53.519
commission

00:29:53.519 --> 00:29:55.190
my angels; I say, 'Angels of

00:29:55.200 --> 00:29:57.310
the Lord, I thank you, you are

00:29:57.320 --> 00:29:58.590
protecting

00:29:58.590 --> 00:29:58.600
us.'And

00:29:58.600 --> 00:30:00.590
I

00:30:00.600 --> 00:30:02.190
commission them from the north, the south,

00:30:02.190 --> 00:30:02.200
the

00:30:02.200 --> 00:30:05.590
east, the west to protect our home today.

00:30:05.600 --> 00:30:07.549
I call my angels—swords and shields

00:30:07.549 --> 00:30:07.559
drawn—to

00:30:07.559 --> 00:30:10.350
watch over us.

00:30:12.279 --> 00:30:14.789
I always give God the

00:30:14.799 --> 00:30:17.149
praise; I never praise an angel. You never

00:30:17.159 --> 00:30:18.710
worship an angel.

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:21.509
They are there to protect you,

00:30:21.519 --> 00:30:22.950
but they are not there to

00:30:22.950 --> 00:30:22.960
be

00:30:22.960 --> 00:30:24.590
worshipped.

00:30:24.600 --> 00:30:26.430
You can

00:30:26.440 --> 00:30:27.990
hang out with Jesus; you hang out with

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:30.190
the Holy Spirit. He's the one that dwells

00:30:30.200 --> 00:30:32.509
on the inside of you.

00:30:38.399 --> 00:30:39.870
How do you know an angel's

00:30:39.880 --> 00:30:41.789
talking to you versus the devil? The

00:30:41.799 --> 00:30:45.350
devil's a fallen angel.

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:54.190
Just don't talk to angels; talk to

00:30:54.200 --> 00:30:57.269
the Holy Spirit.

00:31:17.679 --> 00:31:19.750
I commission my angels all the

00:31:19.760 --> 00:31:22.269
time. 'Go with my children and you protect

00:31:22.279 --> 00:31:24.509
them as they go to this place or that

00:31:24.509 --> 00:31:24.519
place.'I

00:31:24.519 --> 00:31:26.830
thank You, Lord, that

00:31:26.840 --> 00:31:28.230
You're sending angels here with us

00:31:28.240 --> 00:31:30.470
to protect us on the way to church or on

00:31:30.480 --> 00:31:32.950
the way to the grocery store.

00:31:35.159 --> 00:31:36.590
I send my

00:31:36.600 --> 00:31:38.310
angels with my children to protect them

00:31:38.320 --> 00:31:40.470
as they go to school. I thank You, Lord,

00:31:40.480 --> 00:31:43.149
that Psalm 91 says that they will

00:31:43.159 --> 00:31:45.470
bear us up in their hands lest we

00:31:45.480 --> 00:31:47.549
dash our foot against a stone.

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:52.470
They're

00:31:56.840 --> 00:31:59.509
ministering spirits sent for the heirs

00:31:59.519 --> 00:32:02.110
of salvation. I believe with all my

00:32:02.120 --> 00:32:04.350
heart that God's given His angels

00:32:04.360 --> 00:32:07.310
charge over us to protect us.

00:32:13.240 --> 00:32:15.830
I hope that

00:32:15.840 --> 00:32:17.269
blessed you all today.

00:32:23.639 --> 00:32:25.870
I need you all to understand that

00:32:25.880 --> 00:32:27.389
the devil comes to kill, steal, and

00:32:27.399 --> 00:32:28.389
destroy,

00:32:28.399 --> 00:32:30.190
and God said He came that we might have

00:32:30.200 --> 00:32:32.470
life and life more abundantly. I

00:32:32.480 --> 00:32:34.310
want to pray for you all today.

00:32:34.320 --> 00:32:37.310
Oh man, I almost

00:32:37.320 --> 00:32:39.710
said the Lord told me to tell you this

00:32:39.720 --> 00:32:42.669
also. He said, 'Brandon, you're coming to

00:32:42.679 --> 00:32:45.509
the last half of the year. Here we are;

00:32:45.519 --> 00:32:48.789
January's coming. What are you believing

00:32:48.799 --> 00:32:51.710
for in

00:32:51.710 --> 00:32:51.720
2024?'The

00:32:51.720 --> 00:32:55.629
year's not over with.

00:32:55.639 --> 00:32:58.310
Do not give up on what you're

00:32:58.320 --> 00:33:00.310
believing for in

00:33:00.320 --> 00:33:04.430
2024; this is not over. We've got half a

00:33:04.440 --> 00:33:06.590
year left. He said, 'Brandon,

00:33:06.600 --> 00:33:10.029
tell my people to believe for

00:33:10.029 --> 00:33:10.039
bigger.'Believe

00:33:10.039 --> 00:33:13.710
bigger in

00:33:13.720 --> 00:33:16.990
2024. Believe that you can have

00:33:17.000 --> 00:33:19.110
exceedingly, abundantly above all that

00:33:19.120 --> 00:33:22.509
you dare ask or think. I believe with all

00:33:22.519 --> 00:33:26.430
my heart that the better days of

00:33:26.430 --> 00:33:26.440
2024—the

00:33:26.440 --> 00:33:28.990
wealth of the

00:33:29.000 --> 00:33:33.110
sinner—is

00:33:33.120 --> 00:33:34.870
laid up for the

00:33:34.880 --> 00:33:37.230
righteous still yet to come this year.

00:33:37.240 --> 00:33:38.909
There's still something supernatural

00:33:38.919 --> 00:33:40.909
happening. People say,

00:33:40.919 --> 00:33:43.110
'Well, you believe a crash is

00:33:43.110 --> 00:33:43.120
coming?'Not

00:33:43.120 --> 00:33:45.029
before financial blessings for the body

00:33:45.039 --> 00:33:48.789
of Christ. I do not believe that we will

00:33:48.799 --> 00:33:51.629
see a massive crash happen before God's

00:33:51.639 --> 00:33:53.389
blessing for His kids to get us out of

00:33:53.399 --> 00:33:55.950
it. He is not going to allow us to go

00:33:55.960 --> 00:33:59.350
through all the drama if you

00:33:59.360 --> 00:34:01.669
are the remnant and you are seeking Him

00:34:01.679 --> 00:34:04.750
daily. I believe God is going to take

00:34:04.760 --> 00:34:06.909
care of His kids and that He's going to

00:34:06.919 --> 00:34:08.829
provide for us with the supernatural

00:34:08.839 --> 00:34:12.389
harvest before we see all the

00:34:12.399 --> 00:34:14.389
drama.

00:34:14.399 --> 00:34:16.310
He said, 'I've never seen

00:34:16.320 --> 00:34:18.550
the righteous forsaken or his seed

00:34:18.560 --> 00:34:21.829
begging bread.'And I believe with all my

00:34:21.839 --> 00:34:23.270
heart God's going to take care of His

00:34:23.280 --> 00:34:26.310
kids. If you're listening

00:34:26.320 --> 00:34:28.950
to Him on what to do and how to invest,

00:34:28.960 --> 00:34:32.109
I believe great days

00:34:32.119 --> 00:34:36.589
are ahead before a financial shaking

00:34:38.720 --> 00:34:40.230
happens.

00:34:42.919 --> 00:34:45.270
Father, I just thank You for

00:34:45.280 --> 00:34:47.069
every single person that is represented

00:34:47.079 --> 00:34:49.750
here today. I bless them in the name of

00:34:49.760 --> 00:34:52.389
Jesus, and I thank You, Father, for Your

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:55.190
hand on this house. I thank You, Lord, for

00:34:55.200 --> 00:34:57.790
Your hand on their houses. I thank You,

00:34:57.800 --> 00:34:59.750
Lord, that You're protecting us and

00:34:59.760 --> 00:35:01.750
that You watch over us. Father, You

00:35:01.760 --> 00:35:04.030
said that no calamity would come nigh us.

00:35:04.040 --> 00:35:06.589
Father, I thank You, Lord, that we are

00:35:06.599 --> 00:35:08.870
Your children and we hear Your

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:11.230
voice and a stranger's voice we will not

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:14.190
follow. I thank You, Father, that You said

00:35:14.200 --> 00:35:16.109
that You would supply all our needs

00:35:16.119 --> 00:35:18.150
according to Your riches and glory by

00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:20.589
Christ Jesus. I plead the blood of

00:35:20.599 --> 00:35:22.710
Jesus over every single one of us, from

00:35:22.720 --> 00:35:24.270
the top of our heads to the soles of our

00:35:24.280 --> 00:35:27.990
feet. I call us well in Jesus'name. Call

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:30.030
them healed and whole and well. I

00:35:30.040 --> 00:35:31.910
thank You according to Your Word, Father,

00:35:31.920 --> 00:35:35.150
that by Your stripes we are healed. I

00:35:35.160 --> 00:35:36.670
thank You, Lord, that we don't have to

00:35:36.680 --> 00:35:38.670
have sickness and disease in our bodies

00:35:38.680 --> 00:35:41.430
according to Galatians—that Christ

00:35:41.440 --> 00:35:43.270
has redeemed us from the curse of the

00:35:43.280 --> 00:35:45.109
law. I thank You, Lord, that You've

00:35:45.119 --> 00:35:47.710
given us authority over the devil, Father;

00:35:47.720 --> 00:35:49.710
that You said we shall trample on serpents

00:35:49.720 --> 00:35:51.510
and scorpions and nothing shall by any

00:35:51.520 --> 00:35:54.190
means hurt us. I thank You, Lord, that You

00:35:54.200 --> 00:35:57.270
said according to Your Bible,

00:35:57.280 --> 00:35:58.630
Father, that

00:35:58.640 --> 00:36:01.510
greater is He that is in

00:36:01.510 --> 00:36:01.520
us

00:36:01.520 --> 00:36:03.510
than he that is in the world. A thousand

00:36:03.520 --> 00:36:06.190
shall fall at your side and ten thousand at

00:36:06.200 --> 00:36:08.349
your right hand, but nothing shall come

00:36:08.359 --> 00:36:11.109
nigh us. I thank You, Father, that we

00:36:11.119 --> 00:36:13.150
submit ourselves therefore unto God, we

00:36:13.160 --> 00:36:16.150
resist the devil, and he will flee from

00:36:16.160 --> 00:36:19.470
us in Jesus'name. And Father, I thank You,

00:36:19.480 --> 00:36:20.990
Lord, for all those things that You

00:36:21.000 --> 00:36:23.309
promised us in Your scripture. I

00:36:23.319 --> 00:36:25.349
thank You, Lord, that we

00:36:25.359 --> 00:36:27.109
can be the head, not the tail; above and

00:36:27.119 --> 00:36:28.790
not beneath.

00:36:28.800 --> 00:36:30.630
Father, I pray for every single person

00:36:30.640 --> 00:36:32.390
that is watching this

00:36:32.400 --> 00:36:33.990
channel today, and I thank You,

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:36.069
Lord, that they're refreshed

00:36:36.069 --> 00:36:36.079
and

00:36:36.079 --> 00:36:39.630
excited about life. They know

00:36:39.640 --> 00:36:42.829
that You said to believe for bigger.

00:36:42.839 --> 00:36:45.309
Believe for bigger, for

00:36:45.319 --> 00:36:47.270
exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:36:47.280 --> 00:36:50.870
you dare ask or think. I thank You, Father,

00:36:50.880 --> 00:36:53.790
that all our desires of our heart... You

00:36:53.800 --> 00:36:56.190
said You give us the desires of our

00:36:56.200 --> 00:36:59.910
heart. I thank You, Father. I thank You,

00:36:59.920 --> 00:37:02.190
Lord, that we are blessed in the city

00:37:02.200 --> 00:37:05.190
and in the field, coming in and going

00:37:05.200 --> 00:37:09.270
out. This is a good year—that 2024 is going to be a year that

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:11.630
we soar and we go

00:37:11.640 --> 00:37:14.670
even higher with You, and that there

00:37:14.670 --> 00:37:14.680
is

00:37:14.680 --> 00:37:17.390
still half a year left. We

00:37:17.400 --> 00:37:19.510
give You praise for it. All of August,

00:37:19.520 --> 00:37:21.550
September, October, November, and

00:37:21.550 --> 00:37:21.560
December—five

00:37:21.560 --> 00:37:24.109
months. You can do a

00:37:24.119 --> 00:37:27.790
lot in five months.

00:37:27.800 --> 00:37:29.750
So Lord, we give You praise and glory for

00:37:29.760 --> 00:37:32.589
it today. We thank You, Lord, that You

00:37:32.599 --> 00:37:34.589
died on the cross and You rose again on

00:37:34.599 --> 00:37:36.870
the third day and You made it where we

00:37:36.880 --> 00:37:39.270
don't have to go to hell. Father,

00:37:39.280 --> 00:37:41.790
You paid the price for us, and

00:37:41.800 --> 00:37:44.670
Father, we love You and we worship You. We

00:37:44.680 --> 00:37:46.470
give You all the praise and glory for it

00:37:46.480 --> 00:37:49.750
in the mighty name of Jesus. Amen

00:37:49.760 --> 00:37:53.069
and amen. Well, like I said, thank you all

00:37:53.079 --> 00:37:56.109
for joining me. If you could, like

00:37:56.119 --> 00:37:58.349
and subscribe if you're not

00:37:58.359 --> 00:38:01.190
already subscribed. Thank you for

00:38:01.200 --> 00:38:03.950
sticking around.

00:38:03.960 --> 00:38:05.950
Put a smile on your

00:38:05.960 --> 00:38:09.109
face and a song in your heart. Jesus

00:38:09.119 --> 00:38:11.430
loves you so much and we love you, and we

00:38:11.440 --> 00:38:13.589
will see you all next time. God bless you

00:38:13.599 --> 00:38:17.839
all and have a wonderful day. Bye-bye.

